# --- All values must be in arc seconds
# --- All values are with respect to a fiducial pointing center
# --------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 
#
# CORNER SCHEME (must stick to that!)
# 'X' displays the pointing center (not necessarily centered within the FoV) 
