#      /                             \
#     V3                             V6
#     |                               | 
#     |                               | 
#     |                               | 
#     |                          V8---V7 
#     |                          |     
#     |               X          |     (barcode vignetting)
#     |                          |     
#     |                          V9--V10 
#     |                               | 
#     |                               | 
#     |                               | 
#    V2                              V11
#      \                             /
#       \                           /
#       V1 ---------------------- V12
#
#
#
# GAP and DETECTOR ARRAY SCHEME (must stick to that!)
# 'X' displays the pointing center (not necessarily centered within the FoV) 
#
#   X2-Y2 --- X3-Y3
#     |         | 
#     |         | 
#     |         | 
#     |    X    |
#     |         | 
#     |         | 
